page.title: 20CREDITS
page.content: This project was carried out by the children of Tattingstone CEVC Primary School. The Children were 9-11 years old. To do it we went out on walks and in cars, interviewed people, sent out questionnaires and did research work. The children involved were:- Shaun Witt, Scott Matthews, Karl Wykes, Stephanie Williams, wendy Cook, Benjamin Standing, Roy Gayfer, Stephen Cornish, Kevin Marjoram, Joanna Friend, Esther Bennett, Richard Fulcher, Bruce Field, Jason Skilton, Ian Harding, Judith Livermore, Helen Wod, Heidi Schanz and Sarah Chinn. Mrs Williams, Mr Riley and Mrs Dale helped us and Mr Tatchell took the photographs.
